headline: Honeywell may walk away from Johnson Matthey catalyst deal, Bloomberg reports
summary: Investing.com -- Honeywell International Inc (NASDAQ:HON) is weighing whether to abandon its planned acquisition of Johnson Matthey’s Catalyst Technologies business, Bloomberg News reported, citing people familiar with the matter.
